  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if patients have more hypoglycemic episodes the
      first 3 days following pump start compared to their usual number of hypoglycemias with our
      actual pump initiation protocol.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
